TLDR: Mind2Web is introduced, the first dataset for developing and evaluating generalist agents for the web that can follow language instructions to complete complex tasks on any website and an initial exploration of using large language models (LLMs) for building generalist web agents is conducted.},
	keywords = {Computer Science - Computation and Language},
	file = {Preprint PDF:/Users/sugarfly/Zotero/storage/3NRCIKAD/Deng 等 - 2023 - Mind2Web Towards a Generalist Agent for the Web.pdf:application/pdf;Snapshot:/Users/sugarfly/Zotero/storage/DDNYA79M/2306.html:text/html},
