TLDR: The experiments show that GPT-4V with SoM in zero-shot setting outperforms the state-of-the-art fully-finetuned referring expression comprehension and segmentation model on RefCOCOg, and the effectiveness of SoM on a wide range of fine-grained vision and multimodal tasks is validated.},
	keywords = {Computer Science - Artificial Intelligence, Computer Science - Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition, /done, Computer Science - Computation and Language, Computer Science - Human-Computer Interaction},
	file = {Preprint PDF:/Users/sugarfly/Zotero/storage/LXD9JEZE/Yang 等 - 2023 - Set-of-Mark Prompting Unleashes Extraordinary Visual Grounding in GPT-4V.pdf:application/pdf},
